parameters: \n<\N[15]>Humans, why do you spill more blood on these grounds?
\n<\N[15]>To protect this land from your evil.
\n<\N[15]>You have now opened aged old wounds.

name: Dimensional Ice Wizard, Winter Wolf EXP:3417

parameters: \n<\N[17]>These lands do not belong to humans such as you.
\n<\N[1]>But we only want the \C[17]amulet\C[0] this time!
\n<\N[17]>The gears have been set in motion.
\n<\N[18]>WHEN THIS LAND IS CLEANSED, MY PEOPLE SHALL RETURN.
\n<\N[18]>We are to die by the hands of thieves.

name: Skeleton Warrior King, Skeleton Warrior*4 EXP:13297

parameters: \n<\N[19]>You are just a thorn in my side.
\n<\N[4]>FROM NOW ON WE FIGHT TO PROTECT OUR FRIENDS AND FAMILY!
\n<\N[3]>ONLY SOMETHING SO CORRUPT WOULD THINK DEATH IS THE SOLUTION!
\n<\N[19]>THEN YOU ARE ALL JUST LIKE I WASSSSSS!
\n<\N[20]>Witness the power of six hundred years of divine rule!
\n<\N[1]>Ohh no, this whole place is collapsing!?
\n<\N[2]>The teleporter has been smashed, what do we do?
\n<\N[1]>Now to just cut up this little guy and...
\n<\N[1]>Mum will understand, we can just \.\.ration out what we have.
